

# Online Education Website

## 📖 Description

A responsive **Online Education Website** built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.
It features course listings, an about section, and a contact form with offline support.
The project is a **Progressive Web App (PWA)** with caching, background sync, and push notification support.

## 🚀 Features

* Responsive design with smooth navigation
* Courses showcase with images and details


## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (jQuery)
* **PWA Support:** Service Worker, Cache API, Background Sync, Push API

## 📂 Project Structure

```
├── index.html        # Main webpage
├── style.css         # Stylesheet
├── script.js         # Frontend logic
├── service-worker.js # Service worker for PWA features
└── images/           # Project images
